- `off`: Disables the rule.', example='on'),
  ruleName?: string(name='RuleName', description='The name of the rule. This parameter is optional for a global configuration.', example='rule_example'),
  sequence?: int32(name='Sequence', description='The execution priority of the rule. A smaller value indicates a higher priority.', example='1'),
  serveStale?: string(name='ServeStale', description='Controls whether to serve stale content. If enabled, an edge node can serve expired content from its cache if the origin server is unavailable. Valid values:

- `on`: Enables this feature.

- `off`: Disables this feature.', example='on'),
  siteId?: long(name='SiteId', description='The ID of the site. To get this ID, call the [ListSites](~~ListSites~~) operation.

This parameter is required.', example='123456****'),
  sortQueryStringForCache?: string(name='SortQueryStringForCache', description='Controls whether to sort query string parameters when generating a cache key. Valid values:

